//www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/7499673867787561709","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2013年11月5日 16:42:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"A0cHQno5eCp7ImA9XBZVFU8.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-8081301891764345234"},"published":{"$t":"2017-09-28T00:17:13.420+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2017-09-28T00:17:13.420+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2017-09-28T00:17:13.420+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 人民救星金正恩\n同意你所说。\n\n俺在3年前的博文《[url=https://program-t..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 人民救星金正恩<br />同意你所说。<br /><br />俺在3年前的博文《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2013/12/gold-rush-vs-bitcoin-fever.html]回顾历史上的加州淘金热——给比特币矿工的忠告[/url]》，已经警告过那些想当比特币矿工的普通网民。<br /><br />在那篇中，俺还提到“加州淘金热”，情况很类似。<br />类似的景象在历史上反复重演——盲目跟风者，基本上成了牺牲品。<br /><br />另一篇相关的博文是：<br />《[url=https://program-think.blogspot.com/2014/01/misunderstanding-about-making-money.html]为啥急功近利反而赚不到钱——给拜金主义者的忠告[/url]》"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4749619163960271295/comments/default/8081301891764345234?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4749619163960271295/comments/default/8081301891764345234?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/09/Introduction-DHT-Kademlia-Chord.html?showComment=1506529033420#c8081301891764345234","title":"聊聊分布式散列表&#65288;DHT&#65289;的原理&#8212;&#8212;以 Kademlia&#65288;Kad&#65289; 和 Chord 为例"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/4749619163960271295/comments/default/633505955113969745?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/09/Introduction-DHT-Kademlia-Chord.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-4749619163960271295","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/4749619163960271295","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2017年9月28日 00:17:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"A04MQH08fCp7ImA9XR9bF0Q.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-6214888259074676076"},"published":{"$t":"2017-06-30T13:19:41.374+08:00"},"updated":{"$t":"2017-06-30T13:19:41.374+08:00"},"app$edited":{"xmlns$app":"http://www.w3.org/2007/app","$t":"2017-06-30T13:19:41.374+08:00"},"title":{"$t":"TO 请注意安全\n首先，非常感谢对俺的关心，并发了多条安全方面的建议 :)\n对这几条建议，俺一起回复..."},"content":{"type":"html","$t":"TO 请注意安全<br />首先，非常感谢对俺的关心，并发了多条安全方面的建议 :)<br />对这几条建议，俺一起回复如下：<br /><br />========<br /><br />[b]关于博客界面代码[/b]<br />俺【不会】去搞代码混淆。<br />恰恰相反，俺要把代码写得足够通俗，并尽量加注释。<br />甚至俺还会讲解反刷屏机制使用的算法。<br /><br />俺不担心刷屏的家伙找俺算法的漏洞。<br />有漏洞被曝光，俺正好可以继续改进。<br /><br />另，<br />真正懂安全的人，都明白一个道理：【开放】的系统才能做到真正的安全。<br />通过【隐藏】而实现的安全，是不够健壮的。<br /><br />[b]关于保姆的问题[/b]<br />这点大伙儿无需担心。<br />至于为啥无需担心，俺就不解释了。<br /><br />[b]关于输入法[/b]<br />输入法的主要风险在于：<br />很多输入法都有联想功能以及【个性化】的词频库。有时候输入错误，就会暴露打字者的常用词汇/常用习惯。<br /><br />俺如何规避这个风险捏？<br />俺使用【专用的】虚拟机（Guest OS）来操作“编程随想”这个身份。<br />这个 OS 里面的输入法只会用于这个身份。<br /><br />[b]关于周围的同事[/b]<br />早在几年前，俺就说自己是公司的高管。<br />高管是有相应的待遇滴（比如：独立办公室），所以你在 4单元 提到的那几条风险，其实不存在。<br /><br />说到这里，又会有人抱怨俺透露了个人信息。<br />不过捏，天朝有独立办公室的企业管理层，少说也有几万（或十几万）——所以，这个信息量太小了。<br /><br />[b]关于亲人[/b]<br />俺家里人并不知道这个网络身份。<br /><br />[b]关于冷门的技术技能[/b]<br />你提到的几个，俺逐一说一下：<br /><br />熟练emacs、精通lisp<br />这2条基本上是一回事儿。熟悉 emacs 自然熟悉 elisp<br />俺承认这个很小众。<br />不过俺早就不是基层程序员，所以在公司里面用 emacs 的机会并不多。<br /><br />精通linux<br />随着最近十多年的普及，熟悉 Linux 的人非常多。<br /><br />90年代windows程序员<br />在那个年代，大部分程序员都是 Windows 程序员，大部分都是开发桌面应用。<br />有这个经历的群体也很大。"},"link":[{"rel":"edit","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2433693918249050464/comments/default/6214888259074676076?v=2"},{"rel":"self","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2433693918249050464/comments/default/6214888259074676076?v=2"},{"rel":"alternate","type":"text/html","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/06/howto-cover-your-tracks-9.html?showComment=1498799981374#c6214888259074676076","title":"如何隐藏你的踪迹&#65292;避免跨省追捕[9]&#65306;从&#12304;时间角度&#12305;谈谈社会工程学的防范"},{"rel":"related","type":"application/atom+xml","href":"https://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/2433693918249050464/comments/default/789700047088893231?v=2"}],"author":[{"name":{"$t":"编程随想"},"uri":{"$t":"https://www.blogger.com/profile/11741356469378252621"},"email":{"$t":"noreply@blogger.com"},"gd$image":{"rel":"http://schemas.google.com/g/2005#thumbnail","width":"26","height":"32","src":"https://4.bp.blogspot.com/-GTIh2pdzDYI/VtcrB6rX0pI/AAAAAAAABUg/vWdDxEU4N6c/s220/Thinker.jpg?cache=36c4cca294ae50025f1c139a5907df5d"}}],"thr$in-reply-to":{"xmlns$thr":"http://purl.org/syndication/thread/1.0","href":"https://program-think.blogspot.com/2017/06/howto-cover-your-tracks-9.html","ref":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2433693918249050464","source":"http://www.blogger.com/feeds/5235590154125226279/posts/default/2433693918249050464","type":"text/html"},"gd$extendedProperty":[{"name":"blogger.itemClass","value":"pid-1582521586"},{"name":"blogger.displayTime","value":"2017年6月30日 13:19:00"}]},{"gd$etag":"W/\"AkQCQ3oyeSp7ImA9WhBQFEU.\"","id":{"$t":"tag:blogger.com,1999:blog-5235590154125226279.post-2670001654741511322"},"published":{"$t":"2013-03-17T10:46: